Yangtze River dry flow realizes the full coverage of the water green comprehensive service area-Xinhua News Agency Xinhua News Agency Wuhan, December 11 (Reporter Wang Xian) The Fuling Water Green Comprehensive Service Area, Chongqing, was completed on the 10th and put into operation on the 10th.	 After the green integrated service area was listed, the second water green comprehensive service area was officially operated on the upper reaches of the Yangtze River.	 At this point, the water green comprehensive service area has covered the upper, middle and lower reaches of the Yangtze River.	 Qiu Jianhua, deputy director of the Jianghang Authority of the Tsuen River Airlines, said that before, Hubei, Hunan, Jiangxi, Anhui, Jiangsu and other provinces have established 10 water green comprehensive service areas in the middle of the Yangtze River and downstream.	 Promoting the high -quality development of the Yangtze River Shipping played an important role.	 The full coverage of the water green comprehensive service area is another milestone in the construction of green shipping in the Yangtze River. According to reports, the water green integrated service area is an important facilities for the majority of ships and crew to provide comprehensive production and life services to help the majority of crew solve the problem of "urgent and sorrow".	 The two water green integrated service areas upstream of the Yangtze River that are completed this time, integrating living services, production services and government services, with the theme of green and environmental protection, characterized by ship maintenance and ship emergency rescue services, and realizing ships in Hong Kong.	 Po, multiple services "will make crew members who sail in the Yangtze River more efficient and more convenient to live.
